Guy Performs Death Metal Song On ‘The Voice’ Quebec and Is Chosen By Judge posted by Sam Valorose - share 
We've seen many clips of metal heads performing on a variety of talent shows, all to the dismay of both the judges and the audience. Metal is normally used as a joke and punchline on these programs so it's incredible to see it respected like in the video above from The Voice Québec . In the clip, Louis-Paul Gauvreau growls Necrophagist 's "Stabwound" and is actually picked by a judge on national television. { "position1" : { "type" : "artist", "id" : 30417, "name" : "Necrophagist" } } 
